it.emarolab.owloop.descriptor.construction.descriptorExpression

Interface DataPropertyExpression

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Axiom, Axiom.Descriptor<it.emarolab.amor.owlInterface.OWLReferences,org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLDataProperty>, Axiom.Ground<it.emarolab.amor.owlInterface.OWLReferences,org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLDataProperty>, DataProperty<it.emarolab.amor.owlInterface.OWLReferences,org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLDataProperty>, DescriptorGroundInterface<org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLDataProperty>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DataPropertyExpression.Disjoint<D>, DataPropertyExpression.Domain, DataPropertyExpression.Equivalent<D>, DataPropertyExpression.Range, DataPropertyExpression.Sub<D>, DataPropertyExpression.Super<D>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DataPropertyGround, DomainRangeDataPropertyDesc, FullDataPropertyDesc, HierarchicalDataPropertyDesc, RestrictionDataPropertyDesc

    public interface DataPropertyExpression
extends DataProperty<it.emarolab.amor.owlInterface.OWLReferences,org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLDataProperty>, DescriptorGroundInterface<org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLDataProperty>
    This interface extends all the interfaces in DataProperty. It allows to Axiom.Descriptor.readExpressionAxioms() and Axiom.Descriptor.writeExpressionAxioms() specifically for OWL data properties. It contains several expressions that can be combined in any arbitrary way as they rely on the same ground (DataGroundInstance).
